on making low waste estimates at rocky flats they also are accused 
of making false statements regarding waste disposal at the facility 
at that time the plants plutoniumreprocessing facility 
building 771 was supposed to be shut down for four months afer 
three safety inspectors were accidentally exposed to radiation 
but the fbi using infrared cameras during flights over rocky 
flats in december detected burning in an incinerator in building 
771 
meanwhile whiteman and sanchini publicly were saying the 
building totally was shut down 
whiteman and dorr also were accused of misleading regulators in 
1985 by certifying that rocky flats groundwater monitoring system 
complied with federal requirements the affidavit says that 
certification was found to be false and in violation of federal law 
whiteman and other energy department officials were accused of 
claiming that a number of wastes were nonhazardous when in fact 
they were hazardous 
